data.description: Immaculate 4 bedroom 3 bath on 5 secluded unrestricted acres. Granite countertops throughout. Upgrades include New architectural roof high wind, custom Anderson windows high wind, HVAC & duct work dual zoned with separate thermostat, dishwasher, refrigerator, Kohler comfort height toilets, hot water heater, encapsulated crawlspace, underground dog fencing. Master bathroom completely remodeled with high-end jacuzzi and sauna. New storage building with warranty and dual drain lines under driveway for added protection.  Seller offering seller incentive of $5,000 to buyers.
